Function Reference/is preview « WordPress Codex
-----------

Usage
-----

` <?php is_preview(); ?> `

Parameters
----------

Return Values
-------------

 `(boolean)` 
:   True on success, false on failure.

Examples
--------

    if ( ! is_preview() ) {
        // Include analytics code
    }

Notes
-----

Change Log
----------

Since: 2.0.0

Source File
-----------

`is_preview()` is located in `wp-includes/query.php`.

